ch</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Alkesh Miyani\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3478:\"<p>Our most powerful Magazine &amp; News <strong>WordPress theme Ybrant 1.2</strong> is finally arrived with new features. After releasing any new product, we provide product updates with latest features regularly on our website.</p>\n<p>Ybrant is another fully widgetized homepage theme for your news &amp; magazine WordPress website. It was our first ever news and magazine-style theme as we just started diving into a news style theme.</p>\n<p>Let’s take a closer look at some of the new features that makes Ybrant to be absolutely Vibrant.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_21436\" style=\"width: 1030px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Ybrant-Theme-Options-Panel.png\" alt=\"Ybrant - News &amp; Magazine WordPress Theme\" width=\"1020\" height=\"1310\" class=\"size-full wp-image-21436\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Ybrant-Theme-Options-Panel.png 1020w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Ybrant-Theme-Options-Panel-234x300.png 234w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Ybrant-Theme-Options-Panel-768x986.png 768w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Ybrant-Theme-Options-Panel-797x1024.png 797w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Ybrant-Theme-Options-Panel-500x642.png 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Ybrant-Theme-Options-Panel-624x801.png 624w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Ybrant-Theme-Options-Panel-850x1092.png 850w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Ybrant-Theme-Options-Panel-156x200.png 156w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1020px) 100vw, 1020px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ybrant &#8211; Theme Options Panel</p></div>\n<h2>What&#8217;s included in this updates?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>New UI for backend to get better user experience</li>\n<li>New theme option tab added to import/export theme options</li>\n<li>Revised social followers widget with theme option panel</li>\n<li>Added support of Instagram and Pinterest followers count</li>\n<li>Added system status tab that might helpful while asking a support query</li>\n<li>Added Blog Designer PRO plugin support</li>\n</ul>\n<p>On celebration of <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/thanksgiving-deals-black-friday-cyber-monday-sales-2016/\">Thanksgiving Deals 2016</a>, we are providing product updates for all our WordPress themes and plugins. Have a look at our freebies like <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/wordpress-themes/?price_filter=free_pro\" target=\"_blank\">free WordPress themes</a>, <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/wordpress-plugins/?price_filter=free_pro\" target=\"_blank\">free WordPress plugins</a>, <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/magento-2-themes/?price_filter=free_pro\" target=\"_blank\">free Magento 2 theme</a> and <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/magento-2-extensions/?price_filter=free_pro\" target=\"_blank\">free Magento 2 extensions</a>.</p>\n<p>Enjoy your news website with <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/wordpress-themes/ybrant/\">Ybrant 1.2</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/ybrant-news-wordpress-theme-released-with-amazing-features/\">Ybrant 1.2 Out Now &#8211; News WordPress Theme is Updated with New Features</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7: