e last few years of e-commerce market. </p>\n<p>Freely available, <a href=\"http://www.magentocommerce.com/download\" target=\"_blank\">Magento Community Edition</a> should be your choice of e-commerce online store because of its flexibility. Install, edit or use this edition of Magento in any way you like. </p>\n<p>This is the reason why Magento is so popular in web market. Many well known brands like Nike, Samsung and Nestle have successfully emerged in the web market using Magento platform. </p>\n<h2>Magento is globally recognized and preferred e-commerce platform</h2>\n<p>Want to build an e-commerce web store of your choice?</p>\n<p>Then you must opt to <strong>Magento</strong> as your platform for developing a high-quality and robust website. Being a CMS platform, Magento is also featured with various extensions and templates to build a feature-rich and search engine friendly e-commerce website.</p>\n<p>A webstore selling anything, should be looking great to attract visitors along with user friendly features and facilities to make customer&#8217;s shopping experience easy and fun.</p>\n<p>Recently, Magento rolled out Magento 2 version which is enhanced platform for building e-commerce. Let&#8217;s check about all new Magento 2 features and enhancements. </p>\n<h2>Why should you go for Magento 2 instead of Magento 1.x?</h2>\n<p>Any technology have its own pros and cons and so with Magento 2. Listing here are some of the reasons and benefits of using Magento 2 over Magento 1.x</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Staying with modern technologies</li>\n<li>Easy customization facilities for developers</li>\n<li>User-friendly concept</li>\n<li>Component oriented module structure</li>\n<li>Absent, new and changed tables in Magento 2.0</li>\n<li>Quality themes and extensions for Magento 2.0</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Being in web development and design, we are aware of all the web requirements of a customer. We know the capability of Magento 2 and hence we are listing some great Magento 2 free themes and Extensions! </p>\n<p><strong>They are free to download, so why don&#8217;t you try it?</strong></p>\n<h3>1. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-themes/freego-responsive-theme-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\">FreeGo &#8211; Free Responsive theme for Magento® 2</a></h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_17119\" style=\"width: 1150px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/freego-responsive-magento-2-theme.png\" alt=\"FreeGo Free Responsive Theme for Magento 2\" width=\"1140\" height=\"490\" class=\"size-full wp-image-17119\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/freego-responsive-magento-2-theme.png 1140w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/freego-responsive-magento-2-theme-300x129.png 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/freego-responsive-magento-2-theme-768x330.png 768w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/freego-responsive-magento-2-theme-1024x440.png 1024w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/freego-responsive-magento-2-theme-500x215.png 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/freego-responsive-magento-2-theme-624x268.png 624w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/freego-responsive-magento-2-theme-850x365.png 850w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/freego-responsive-magento-2-theme-350x150.png 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1140px) 100vw, 1140px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">FreeGo &#8211; Responsive Magento 2 Theme</p></div>\n<p>The first name in this list of free themes is a <strong>FreeGo</strong>.</p>\n<p>This Magento 2 theme offers number of premium value features like Featured Product List, Off Canvas Menu, Child Theme Ready, Advanced Theme Options Panel, Gallery Image, One Step Checkout, Font Awesome, Inherited From Blank Theme, Off Canvas Menu, etc. </p>\n<p>With so many useful features, this free theme is definitely your pick but if you want more options, you can extend this free premium value to more via adding supported Magento 2 extensions. </p>\n<h4>List of Magento 2 Extensions supported with FreeGo theme (Tried and tested by our team)</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/advanced-blog-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\">Advanced Blog</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/mega-menu-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\">Mega Menu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/responsive-banner-slider-magento-2-extension/\" target=\"_blank\">Responsive Banner Slider</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/advanced-newsletter-popup-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\">Advanced Newsletter Popup</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/shop-by-brand-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\">Shop By Brand</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/advanced-testimonials-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\">Advanced Testimonial</a></li>\n<li>and all other <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/magento-2-extensions/\" target=\"_blank\">Magento 2 Extensions</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>2. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/easy-contact-form-widget-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\">Easy Contact Form Widget &#8211; Extension for Magento® 2</a></h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_16609\" style=\"width: 1150px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/easy-contact-form-widget-magento-2-extension.jpg\" alt=\"Easy Contact Form Widget - Free Magento 2 Extension\" width=\"1140\" height=\"490\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16609\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/easy-contact-form-widget-magento-2-extension.jpg 1140w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/easy-contact-form-widget-magento-2-extension-300x129.jpg 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/easy-contact-form-widget-magento-2-extension-768x330.jpg 768w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/easy-contact-form-widget-magento-2-extension-1024x440.jpg 1024w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/easy-contact-form-widget-magento-2-extension-500x215.jpg 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/easy-contact-form-widget-magento-2-extension-624x268.jpg 624w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/easy-contact-form-widget-magento-2-extension-850x365.jpg 850w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/easy-contact-form-widget-magento-2-extension-350x150.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1140px) 100vw, 1140px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Easy Contact Form Widget &#8211; Free Magento 2 Extension</p></div>\n<p>Contact forms play important role in letting customers contact you for any suggestions or queries. If you want customer interaction with you, use this Magento 2 extension, contact/inquiry form.</p>\n<p><strong>Easy Contact Form Widget extension</strong> enables the visitor to submit their details of inquiry/feedback in the provided form to the store. You can easily enable/disable Google reCaptcha within the contact form to avoid spamming.</p>\n<p>Build a good customer relationship with nice contact form. Easy to add this widget on any static page, it also offers facility to set custom email template for contact inquiry.</p>\n<h4>Key Features of Easy Contact Form Widget Extension:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Magento 2 ready widget</li>\n<li>Google reCaptha supported</li>\n<li>Ready to add form within any CMS page</li>\n<li>Contact form can be added to sidebar</li>\n<li>Custom email template for contact inquiry</li>\n<li>Dynamic form title and message</li>\n<li>100% open source</li>\n<li>Easy to install and manage</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>3. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/scroll-to-top-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\">Scroll to Top &#8211; Extension for Magento® 2</a></h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_14407\" style=\"width: 1150px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/scroll-to-top-magento-2-extension.jpg\" alt=\"Scroll To Top - Magento 2 Extension\" width=\"1140\" height=\"490\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14407\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/scroll-to-top-magento-2-extension.jpg 1140w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/scroll-to-top-magento-2-extension-300x129.jpg 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/scroll-to-top-magento-2-extension-768x330.jpg 768w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/scroll-to-top-magento-2-extension-1024x440.jpg 1024w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/scroll-to-top-magento-2-extension-500x215.jpg 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/scroll-to-top-magento-2-extension-624x268.jpg 624w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/scroll-to-top-magento-2-extension-850x365.jpg 850w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/scroll-to-top-magento-2-extension-350x150.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1140px) 100vw, 1140px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Scroll To Top &#8211; Magento 2 Extension</p></div>\n<p>So your store has too many things or items to show on single page. It is very frustrating to scroll manually when you arrived at the bottom of the page. Offer your customers, a back to top button with this free Magento 2 Extension Scroll to Top.</p>\n<p><strong>Scroll To Top extension</strong> will help you to put a nice button which will allow customers to scroll up page from bottom to top with one simple click. Don&#8217;t worry, the button is not going to mess with your web page design as it appears only, when the page is scrolled down. This extension requires no code modification in Magento 2 core files. </p>\n<p>Easily set image for scroll to top link from admin settings. Give your visitors a smooth scrolling from bottom to top with this free extension.</p>\n<h4>Key Features of Scroll to Top Extension:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>One Click &#8211; Easy move to top</li>\n<li>Various scrolling effects</li>\n<li>Position selection &#8211; Left or Right</li>\n<li>Custom text option as flexibility</li>\n<li>Custom options like text and BG color</li>\n<li>Custom image instead of text</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>4. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/featured-products/\" target=\"_blank\">Featured Products &#8211; Extension for Magento® 2</a></h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_14414\" style=\"width: 1150px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/features-products-magento-2-extension.jpg\" alt=\"Featured Products - Magento 2 Extension\" width=\"1140\" height=\"490\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14414\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/features-products-magento-2-extension.jpg 1140w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/features-products-magento-2-extension-300x129.jpg 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/features-products-magento-2-extension-768x330.jpg 768w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/features-products-magento-2-extension-1024x440.jpg 1024w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/features-products-magento-2-extension-500x215.jpg 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/features-products-magento-2-extension-624x268.jpg 624w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/features-products-magento-2-extension-850x365.jpg 850w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/features-products-magento-2-extension-350x150.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1140px) 100vw, 1140px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Featured Products &#8211; Magento 2 Extension</p></div>\n<p>Do you want to offer some of the best products to be displayed in a particular section? Now it is easy to showcase your special products with <strong>Magento 2 Featured Products extension</strong>. </p>\n<p>This extension will offer featured products on store in an eye-catching and attractive way. Featuring your handpicked best items to highlight them for customers is a great way to achieve sales. </p>\n<p>Use this extension and display a specified number of products in a grid layout with thumbnails of your products. With admin panel, it is easy to set any product as featured product. Choose “Yes” in the “Featured” attribute, and it will show in featured section on front side.</p>\n<h4>Key Features of Featured Products Extension:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fully customizable interface</li>\n<li>Rich configurable options</li>\n<li>100% open source</li>\n<li>Show in sidebar</li>\n<li>Show in CMS pages</li>\n<li>Use as a widget in any block section</li>\n<li>Support directly add to cart</li>\n<li>Increase store sales</li>\n<li>Eye cooling featured layout and functionality</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/sold-out-label-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\">Sold Out Label &#8211; Extension for Magento® 2</a></h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_16752\" style=\"width: 1150px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sold-out-label-magento-2-extension.jpg\" alt=\"Sold Out Label - Magento 2 Extension\" width=\"1140\" height=\"490\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16752\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sold-out-label-magento-2-extension.jpg 1140w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sold-out-label-magento-2-extension-300x129.jpg 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sold-out-label-magento-2-extension-768x330.jpg 768w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sold-out-label-magento-2-extension-1024x440.jpg 1024w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sold-out-label-magento-2-extension-500x215.jpg 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sold-out-label-magento-2-extension-624x268.jpg 624w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sold-out-label-magento-2-extension-850x365.jpg 850w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sold-out-label-magento-2-extension-350x150.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1140px) 100vw, 1140px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sold Out Label &#8211; Magento 2 Extension</p></div>\n<p>Well, this is another very useful Magento 2 extension. </p>\n<p>Our <strong>Magento 2 Sold Out Label Extension</strong> is a smart extension which automatically displays sold out label over the default image for products with quantity reach to zero. </p>\n<p>This creates a positive impact on visitors that the website is up-to-date in terms of stock. It is your choice whether you want to show label as image or text. </p>\n<p>Moreover, you can also define position of the label like Top Left, Top Center, Top Right, Middle Left, Middle Center, Bottom Left, etc. </p>\n<p>In addition this extension also provide options to set width and height of the label so it will fit perfectly on product images. It is advisable not to remove or delete the product and show 404 not found page to customers. It is bad practice for SEO and customers. This extension comes to the rescue when you are in that Out Of Stock situation.</p>\n<h4>Key Features of Sold Out Label Extension:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Easy installation</li>\n<li>Shows automatically when quantity is zero</li>\n<li>Allow select image as sold out label</li>\n<li>Facility to set width and height for label</li>\n<li>Provide options to set text or image</li>\n<li>Allow set position for label</li>\n<li>Support multi-store</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Conclusion</h3>\n<p>So, you know these many benefits of Magento 2 free themes and extensions. In order to get most out of all the opportunities offered by e-commerce store, Magento and its awesome feature-rich extensions is a right decision. </p>\n<p>At Solwin Infotech, our team can help you with the <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/magento-customization/\" target=\"_blank\">Magento web development and customization</a>.<br />\nFeel free to <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/contact-us/\">contact us</a> to know more on how we can create a solid e-commerce web store using Magento.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/top-free-magento-2-themes-extensions/\">Top Free Magento 2 Theme and Extensions For Your Magento Store</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/top-free-magento-2-themes-extensions/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"5\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:95:\"How to Add WordPress Blog in Your Magento Store With Blog Designer Plugin? (Step-By-Step Guide)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base