rting from <strong>28th October to 2nd November</strong>.</p>\n<p>Enjoy this double dose of festivities with an amazing and power packed bundle of happiness for your websites. Get your first purchase with flat <strong>40% discount</strong> and on next purchase you will get <strong>60% discount</strong> from the vault of our <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/\">product store</a>. This offer applies to our premium collection of WordPress themes and plugins, Magento 1.x &amp; 2.x themes and extensions. Solwin infotech made numerous <strong>WordPress &amp; Magento themes</strong>, <strong>plugins</strong> and <strong>extensions</strong> for various business and blogs such as food portal, fashion, restaurant, woocommerce, portfolio, medical, consultant, reservation booking and many more website.</p>\n<p>No worry if you are looking to buy <strong>multiple items</strong> and haven&#8217;t registered with site, you will automatically become existing user after your first premium order. </p>\n<div class=\"highlight_strip\" style=\"margin-top: 5px;font-size: 25px\">No coupon code required, Discount auto-apply on checkout.<br /><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">Valid up to 12th Nov. 2016</span></div>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> This offer is not available for our codecanyon products &#8211; <a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/blog-designer-pro-for-wordpress/17069678/?ref=solwin\" target=\"_blank\">Blog Designer PRO</a> and <a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/user-activity-log-pro-for-wordpress/18201203?ref=solwin\" target=\"_blank\">User Activity Log PRO</a>.</p>\n<h2>What about Support?</h2>\n<p>As we have short holiday vacation and all team members will be in mood of enjoying it, but few of us will try to reply of support tickets. (It may happen that our reply will be delayed or we will provide limited support during Diwali Vacation).</p>\n<p>To avoid misunderstand while providing support for support ticket during <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/celebrating-diwali-2016-flat-40-discount-offer/\" target=\"_blank\">Diwali offer deals</a> please follow below guidelines. So, it helps to reduce the number of replies iteration to resolve the issue. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Mention your Url properly.</li>\n<li>Describe your issuse or bug in brief.</li>\n<li>Take appropriate snap where you find support and mention the change or little description below it.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"quotes\" style=\"color: #ff9900;line-height: 46px;font-size: 30px\">Don&#8217;t forget to grab Amazing deal&#8230;!</span></p>\n<p>So here’s wishing you all a Happy Diwali and Happy New Year.</p>\n<p>Enjoy!!!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/celebrating-diwali-2016-flat-40-discount-offer/\">Celebrating Diwali 2016 with Flat 40% Discount Offer</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/celebrating-diwali-2016-flat-40-discount-offer/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"Free Set of Theme Hacks to Make Your Theme Compatible With Blog Designer PRO Plugi