{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"New Update Kosmic Magento 2 Theme\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=17045\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:653:\"<p>Almost six months completed to our first ever Magento 2 theme Kosmic, and it still continues to be one of our most popular theme. During this last 6 months we’ve released numerous updates with new features and possibilities in the theme. But now we&#8217;re going to release the most significant update and launch of Kosmic [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/magento/kosmic-magento-2-theme-ready-to-launch-with-massive-update/\">Kosmic 2.0 Magento 2 Theme is Ready to Launch with Massive Update</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Sanjay Dabhoya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14180:\"<p>Almost six months completed to our first ever <strong>Magento 2 theme Kosmic</strong>, and it still continues to be one of our most popular theme. During this last 6 months we’ve released numerous updates with new features and possibilities in the theme. But now we&#8217;re going to release the most significant update and launch of <strong>Kosmic 2.0</strong> Magento 2 Theme.</p>\n<p>Kosmic 2.0 is strengthened with brand new features like Mega Menu, Unlimited Color Options, New Header Layout, More Styles For Products And Custom Features, New Social Widget Like Instagram and Flickr.</p>\n<p>It becomes easy now for any store owner to build attractive eCommerce site with just one single theme.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_21544\" style=\"width: 830px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/kosmic-v2-magento-2-theme.png\" alt=\"Kosmic v2.0 - Magento 2 Theme\" width=\"820\" height=\"352\" class=\"size-full wp-image-21544\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/kosmic-v2-magento-2-theme.png 820w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/kosmic-v2-magento-2-theme-300x129.png 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/kosmic-v2-magento-2-theme-768x330.png 768w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/kosmic-v2-magento-2-theme-500x215.png 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/kosmic-v2-magento-2-theme-624x268.png 624w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/kosmic-v2-magento-2-theme-350x150.png 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kosmic v2.0 &#8211; Magento 2 Theme</p></div>\n<p>Have a look at the new <a href=\"http://demo.solwininfotech.com/magento2/kosmic\">Kosmic 2.0 Demo →</a></p>\n<hr style=\"margin: 35px 0 45px !important;float:left;width: 90%\" />\n<h3>What’s New in Kosmic 2.0 Magento 2 Theme?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Mega Menu</strong> Extension</li>\n<li><strong>Unlimited Color</strong> Options</li>\n<li>More Configuration Options</li>\n<li>Multi Language Support</li>\n<li>Box/Full Width Layout</li>\n<li><strong>New Header</strong> Type</li>\n<li><strong>Instagram</strong> Widget</li>\n<li><strong>Flickr</strong> Widget</li>\n<li>Best Deals Widget</li>\n<li>Useful Static Blocks</li>\n<li>Sticky Menu</li>\n<li>Page Loader</li>\n<li>Footer Google Map</li>\n<li>Alternate Product Image Feature</li>\n<li>Header and Footer Improvements</li>\n<li>More Styles for Product List</li>\n<li>Update Scroll To Top Extension</li>\n<li>Quantity Increment</li>\n<li>Fix Responsive Issues</li>\n</ul>\n<p>and many more!</p>\n<hr style=\"margin: 35px 0 45px !important;float:left;width: 90%\" />\n<p><strong>Mega Menu with Kosmic</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/mega-menu-300x149.png\" alt=\"Kosmic Mega Menu\" width=\"300\" height=\"149\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-18558\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/mega-menu-300x149.png 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/mega-menu-500x248.png 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/mega-menu-350x173.png 350w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/mega-menu.png 555w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /> Mega Menu extension official version is bundled with Kosmic. To display a dynamic and professional content with Kosmic theme, store must have a Mega Menu. With Magento 2 Mega Menu extension, store owner can display dynamic categories and sub-categories in a multi-column drop down menu. In addition, store owner can promote items, banners and clips right in the Mega Menu.</p>\n<hr style=\"margin: 35px 0 45px !important;float:left;width: 90%\" />\n<p><strong>Unlimited Color Options</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Kosmic-Multi_color-Features-300x149.png\" alt=\"Kosmic Multi color Features\" width=\"300\" height=\"149\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-14912\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Kosmic-Multi_color-Features-300x149.png 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Kosmic-Multi_color-Features-500x248.png 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Kosmic-Multi_color-Features.png 555w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /> Store owners can paint their store with whatever color they want. The color choice is unlimited, and they can specify it via backend panel. There are 6 pre-defined color patterns created for everyone but you can change that colors according to your requirements anytime.</p>\n<hr style=\"margin: 35px 0 45px !important;float:left;width: 90%\" />\n<p><strong>Box/wide Layouts</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Box-layout-300x149.png\" alt=\"Kosmic Box/Wide Layout\" width=\"300\" height=\"149\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-21539\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Box-layout-300x149.png 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Box-layout-500x248.png 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Box-layout-350x173.png 350w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Box-layout.png 555w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /> Set your theme in boxed layout as well as full width layout that fits your store. We understood your requirements, if you are willing to go with old design concepts than box layout is for you. Switch between box and wide layout anytime, there is no limitation and you may never face any issue with responsive also.</p>\n<hr style=\"margin: 35px 0 45px !important;float:left;width: 90%\" />\n<p><strong>Design Panel</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Kosmic_Powerful_Backend_Features-300x149.png\" alt=\"Kosmic Powerful Backend Features\" width=\"300\" height=\"149\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-14916\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Kosmic_Powerful_Backend_Features-300x149.png 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Kosmic_Powerful_Backend_Features-500x248.png 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Kosmic_Powerful_Backend_Features.png 555w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /> Lots of options neatly organized into sections that allows you to design store without any coding knowledge. Think about design changes and you may get feature availability with backend panel. Just play with design panel and you will decorate your website more and more.</p>\n<hr style=\"margin: 35px 0 45px !important;float:left;width: 90%\" />\n<p><strong>New Header Layout</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/multiple-header-type-300x149.png\" alt=\"Multiple Header Style\" width=\"300\" height=\"149\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-18559\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/multiple-header-type-300x149.png 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/multiple-header-type-500x248.png 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/multiple-header-type-350x173.png 350w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/multiple-header-type.png 555w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /> It provides new unique header style that you can easily set for your online store. Center logo &amp; menu, Left/Right position of logo with Header area, etc. are key feature changes with header layout changes.</p>\n<hr style=\"margin: 35px 0 45px !important;float:left;width: 90%\" />\n<p><strong>Footer Google Map</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Footer-Google-Map-300x149.png\" alt=\"Kosmic Footer Google Map\" width=\"300\" height=\"149\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-21540\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Footer-Google-Map-300x149.png 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Footer-Google-Map-500x248.png 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Footer-Google-Map-350x173.png 350w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Footer-Google-Map.png 555w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /> By Default Magento doesn&#8217;t give this functionality to show Google Map in Magento 2 store. This theme provides options to set Google Map on contact page as well as in footer section in eye-catching way.</p>\n<hr style=\"margin: 35px 0 45px !important;float:left;width: 90%\" />\n<p><strong>New Widgets</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/social-widget-300x149.png\" alt=\"Kosmic Instagram and Flickr\" width=\"300\" height=\"149\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-18560\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/social-widget-300x149.png 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/social-widget-500x248.png 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/social-widget-350x173.png 350w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/social-widget.png 555w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /> Kosmic 2.0 comes with 3 new widgets such as <strong><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/instagram-widget-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a></strong>, <strong><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/flickr-widget-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\">Flickr</a></strong> and <strong><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/best-deals-special-products-with-countdown-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\">Best Deals</a></strong>. These are new Magento 2 Extensions and we just published it for all.</p>\n<hr style=\"margin: 35px 0 45px !important;float:left;width: 90%\" />\n<p><strong>Category Page Update</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Category-page-update-300x149.png\" alt=\"Kosmic Category Page Update\" width=\"300\" height=\"149\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-21541\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Category-page-update-300x149.png 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Category-page-update-500x248.png 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Category-page-update-350x173.png 350w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Category-page-update.png 555w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /> Latest version of Kosmic includes some category page changes like more styles for product list, Flip product images, etc. You can select any category page design at once and you may have unique design for category page against other store websites.</p>\n<hr style=\"margin: 35px 0 45px !important;float:left;width: 90%\" />\n<p><strong>Improved Footer Layout</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Improved-Footer-Layout-300x149.png\" alt=\"Kosmic Improved Footer Layout\" width=\"300\" height=\"149\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-21542\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Improved-Footer-Layout-300x149.png 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Improved-Footer-Layout-500x248.png 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Improved-Footer-Layout-350x173.png 350w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Improved-Footer-Layout.png 555w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />Store owner can easily change the appearance of footer styles with custom blocks like 3-4 column, etc. And also you can add your favorite social icons to link your store with social media.</p>\n<hr style=\"margin: 35px 0 45px !important;float:left;width: 90%\" />\n<p><strong>Lots of Statics Blocks</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Lots-of-statics-blocks-300x149.png\" alt=\"Kosmic Lots of statics blocks\" width=\"300\" height=\"149\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-21543\" srcset=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Lots-of-statics-blocks-300x149.png 300w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Lots-of-statics-blocks-500x248.png 500w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Lots-of-statics-blocks-350x173.png 350w, https://www.solwininfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Lots-of-statics-blocks.png 555w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />Lots of static blocks are added with the new version of this theme. Store owner can include promotions, banners or other activities on their online store.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Start creating your new Magento 2 eCommerce store today with <a href=\"http://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-themes/kosmic-multipurpose-responsive-magento-2-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Kosmic 2.0</a> Magento 2 theme. You can also check a wide range of compatible <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/magento-2-extensions/\" target=\"_blank\">Magento 2 extensions</a> for your eCommerce store.</p>\n<p>Checkout the new Kosmic theme now..!!</p>\n<div class=\"highlight_strip\" style=\"margin-top: 5px;background-color: #fcfbe3\"><span>For more information about Kosmic theme see <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-themes/kosmic-multipurpose-responsive-magento-2-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">theme page</a> or take a look at the <a href=\"http://demo.solwininfotech.com/magento2/kosmic\" target=\"_blank\">live demo</a>.</span></div>\n<p>Subscribe our Newsletter and participate with us for the latest updates and freebies on <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/magento-2-themes/\" target=\"_blank\">Magento 2 Themes</a>. Feel free to send your thoughts and feedbacks with comment section below.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/magento/kosmic-magento-2-theme-ready-to-launch-with-massive-update/\">Kosmic 2.0 Magento 2 Theme is Ready to Launch with Massive Update</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:108:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/magento/kosmic-magento-2-theme-ready-to-launch-with-massive-update/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:36:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:17:{s:6:\"server\";s:5:\"nginx\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Tue, 28 Feb 2017 22:31:53 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:14:\"content-length\";s:5:\"29064\";s:15:\"x-cache-enabled\";s:5:\"False\";s:7:\"expires\";s:29:\"Thu, 19 Nov 1981 08:52:00 GMT\";s:13:\"cache-control\";s:62:\"no-store, no-cache, must-revalidate, post-check=0, pre-check=0\";s:6:\"pragma\";s:8:\"no-cache\";s:4:\"etag\";s:34:\"\"0952856253b44b6e7