(358, 198, 'panels_data', 'a:3:{s:7:\"widgets\";a:5:{i:0;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:801:\"<strong>Are you or your child struggling with math? I am an experienced, professional, and compassionate math tutor.</strong>\n\nLet’s work together to help you achieve your goals, whether that be preparing for your next math test, completing homework, raising your grade, or a better and more thorough understanding of the material.\n\nI have a warm personality, and I foster an environment where students feel safe to try, make mistakes, and truly learn. Learning and helping others to learn is my passion.\n\nYou don’t have to struggle anymore! I tutor:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Middle School Math</li>\n 	<li>Algebra 1</li>\n 	<li>Algebra 2</li>\n 	<li>Geometry</li>\n 	<li>PreCalculus</li>\n 	<li>Calculus 1</li>\n 	<li>AP Calculus AB</li>\n 	<li>College Algebra</li>\n 	<li>Test Prep (ACT, SAT, GED, and GRE)</li>\n</ul>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:4:\"html\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"57e04bb654755\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:0;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"eeb5dc2a-0811-45bf-9007-032b4ab73f05\";s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:1;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:385:\"I’ve been coming to Katie for tutoring for quite some time, and she’s finally seeing me out the door. I truly have her to thank for my success in my math courses. She has me walking away with confidence and understanding that just wasn’t there prior to our sessions. She’s always patient, kind and helpful. She makes learning the way it should be – FUN. Thanks again, Katie. \";s:4:\"name\";s:4:\"Anna\";s:6:\"byline\";s:23:\"College Algebra, Online\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:27:\"spacious_testimonial_widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:1;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"9e6219e