nce tutoring over 200 students</li>\n 	<li>ACT: 35 (Math: 36, Science: 36, English: 35, Reading: 33) 99th percentile</li>\n 	<li>GRE Quantitative: 170 (GRE Verbal: 164) 99th percentile</li>\n</ul>\n<h5></h5>\n<h5>And just for fun:</h5>\n- I love local food. I spent a year in Spokane through <a href=\"https://jvcnorthwest.org/\" target=\"_blank\">JVC Northwest</a> working on <a href=\"http://www.catholiccharitiesfoodforall.org/\" target=\"_blank\">food access</a>. I now work at my <a href=\"http://www.montavillamarket.org/\" target=\"_blank\">neighborhood farmers market</a> in Portland crunching numbers and supporting our awesome community of volunteers.\n\n- I love nature and plan on hiking 460 miles of the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pacific_Crest_Trail\" target=\"_blank\">PCT</a> in 2018.\n\n- I\'ve had four concussions, three in 2016, and am passionate about education around care of concussions and <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Post-concussion_syndrome\" target=\"_blank\">post-concussion syndrome</a>.\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:0;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"da1f242c-6bb9-4344-be1f-658ebbea2f1c\";s:5:\"style\";a:0:{}}}i:1;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:200:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-200\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/IMG_2236-e1474320425233.jpg\" alt=\"Katie the Math Tutor\" width=\"2064\" height=\"536\" /></p>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"57e058b3705e7\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:1;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"7871ec73-902e-4d55-836c-244f169fb0ff\";s:5:\"style\";a:2:{s:27:\"background_image_attachment\";b:0;s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}