(658, 10, 'panels_data', 'a:3:{s:7:\"widgets\";a:7:{i:0;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:230:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-374\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Online-Math-Tutor-Katie-Tutors-Math-2.jpeg\" alt=\"Online Math Tutor Katie Tutors Math\" width=\"1400\" height=\"409\" /></p>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"58936be0ef9df\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:0;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"20f816b0-e64c-47b1-8faa-f9da88b5e154\";s:5:\"style\";a:4:{s:27:\"background_image_attachment\";b:0;s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:17:\"iw-visible-screen\";s:6:\"iw-all\";s:17:\"iw-visible-layout\";s:6:\"iw-all\";}}}i:1;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:1563:\"<p><strong>Are you or your child struggling with math? I am an experienced, professional, and compassionate math tutor.</strong></p><p>Let’s work together to help you achieve your goals, whether that be preparing for your next math test, completing homework, raising your grade, or a better and more thorough understanding of the material.</p><p>I have a warm personality, and I foster an environment where students feel safe to try, make mistakes, and truly learn. Learning and helping others to learn is my passion.</p><p>I love making math understandable for students and fostering an environment where students develop a growth mindset and gain confidence in their math skills and their ability to do hard things.</p><p>We use Skype or Google Hangouts to see and hear each other and an online whiteboard (scribblar) to see what the other person is writing in real time.</p><p>You don’t have to struggle anymore! I tutor:</p><ul><li>Middle School Math</li><li>Prealgebra</li><li>Algebra 1</li><li>Algebra 2</li><li>PreCalculus</li><li>Calculus 1</li><li>AP Calculus AB</li><li>College Algebra</li></ul><h