(72, 1, '2016-08-09 17:41:33', '2016-08-10 00:41:33', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Are you or your child struggling with math? I am an experienced, professional, and compassionate math tutor.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Let’s work together to help you achieve your goals, whether that be preparing for your next math test, completing homework, raising your grade, or a better and more thorough understanding of the material.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">I have a warm personality, and I foster an environment where students feel safe to try, make mistakes, and truly learn. Learning and helping others to learn is my passion.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">I love making math understandable for students and fostering an environment where students develop a growth mindset and gain confidence in their math skills and their ability to do hard things.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">We use Skype or Google Hangouts to see and hear each other and an online whiteboard (scribblar) to see what the other person is writing in real time.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">You don’t have to struggle anymore! I tutor:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Middle School Math</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Prealgebra</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Algebra 1 &amp; 2</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Trigonometry</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">PreCalculus</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Calculus 1</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">AP Calculus AB</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">College Algebra</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">GED Math Prep</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-110\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1695px) 100vw, 1695px\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123.jpg 1695w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123-254x300.jpg 254w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123-768x906.jpg 768w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123-868x1024.jpg 868w\" alt=\"Math Tutor Calculator Studying\" width=\"1695\" height=\"2000\" />\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Rates</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>60 minute session - $60</li>\r\n 	<li>30 minute session - $32</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Requirements for online tutoring:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Computer with a Webcam, Microphone, &amp; Skype</li>\r\n 	<li>Reliable Internet Connection</li>\r\n 	<li>Optional: <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2cYXZVq\">Wacom Tablet</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Ready to get started?</h3>\r\nSchedule your free 30-minute consultation today\r\n\r\n<a class=\"call-to-action-button\" title=\"Schedule\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/free-consultation/\">Schedule</a>\r\n\r\nI’ve been coming to Katie for tutoring for quite some time, and she’s finally seeing me out the door. I truly have her to thank for my success in my math courses. She has me walking away with confidence and understanding that just wasn’t there prior to our sessions. She’s always patient, kind and helpful. She makes learning the way it should be – FUN. Thanks again, Katie.\r\n\r\nAnna\r\nCollege Algebra, Online\r\n\r\nSimply the best! Katie is a very knowledgeable and extremely patient tutor. She is a huge part of me understanding and getting through Calc 1. HIGHLY RECOMMENDED!!!\r\n\r\nRussell\r\nCollege Calculus, Returning Adult Student', 'Tutoring', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tutoring', '', '', '2017-02-02 11:23:03', '2017-02-02 19:23:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/?page_id=72', 0, 'page', '', 0),
