(105, 1, '2016-08-09 22:14:54', '2016-08-10 05:14:54', 'Tutoring is a privilege.\r\n<h4><strong>As a math tutor, I witness a student\'s willingness to be vulnerable and make mistakes.</strong></h4>\r\nI walk alongside them in that vulnerable place where learning and growth happen.\r\n\r\nI don\'t take this lightly.\r\n\r\nFrankly, it\'s a <em>sacred</em> space.\r\n\r\nAnd sure, the acquisition of knowledge is great, but what I relish in is the increase in self-confidence and self-efficacy, and the growth in a willingness to try.\r\n\r\nAnd I love math.\r\n<h2>You see, the thing is, <strong>I think math is fun.</strong></h2>\r\nIt\'s like a game or puzzle that I get to play with. There is one right answer, so I know when I\'m on track, but there are always many many ways to arrive at that answer, many ways to think about it and make it make sense in my brain. It\'s so fun.\r\n\r\nAnd <strong>I love sharing this</strong> with other people.\r\n\r\nBecause I think after I do, you might think math is fun too.\r\n\r\n<em>Or, at least, you won\'t think it\'s so hard.</em>\r\n\r\nBecause math doesn\'t have to be hard.\r\n\r\nHas it felt hard?\r\n\r\nLet\'s get you a guide.\r\n<h5>A tutor.</h5>\r\nSomeone who knows when to nudge, when to sit in silence and wait to let your brain make the connection, when to support, affirm, or encourage.\r\n\r\n<em>Ahem,</em> that\'s me.\r\n\r\nI\'m a great listener, highly empathetic, and have a great intuitive sense combined with thousands of hours of experience to know how you learn best in each moment.\r\n\r\nIf this sounds like something you are jiving with, schedule a <a href=\"https://katietutorsmath.acuityscheduling.com/schedule.php?appointmentType=1728850\">New Student Consultation</a>.', 'My Philosophy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-09 22:14:54', '2016-08-10 05:14:54', '', 17, 'http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
