(147, 1, '2016-08-23 00:37:27', '2016-08-23 07:37:27', 'Tutoring math is a privilege.\r\n<h4><strong>As a math tutor, I witness a student\'s willingness to be vulnerable and make mistakes.</strong></h4>\r\nI walk alongside them in that tender place where learning and growth happen.\r\n<h5>I don\'t take this lightly.</h5>\r\nFrankly, it\'s a <em>sacred</em> space.\r\n\r\nAnd sure, the acquisition of knowledge is great, but what I relish in is the increase in self-confidence and self-efficacy, and the growth in a willingness to try.\r\n\r\nAnd, I love math.\r\n<h3>You see, the thing is, <strong>I think math is fun.</strong></h3>\r\nIt\'s like a game or puzzle I get to play with. There is one right answer, so I know when I\'m on track, but there are always many, many ways to arrive at that answer, many ways to think about it and play with it. It\'s. so. fun.\r\n\r\nAnd <strong>I love sharing this</strong> with other people.\r\n\r\nBecause I think after I do, you might think math is fun too.\r\n\r\n<em>Or, at least, you won\'t think it\'s so hard.</em>\r\n\r\nBecause math doesn\'t have to be hard.\r\n\r\nHas it felt hard?\r\n\r\nLet\'s get you a guide.\r\n<h5>A tutor.</h5>\r\nSomeone who knows when to nudge, when to sit in silence and wait to let your brain make the connection, when to support, affirm, or encourage.\r\n\r\n<em>Ahem,</em> that\'s me.\r\n\r\nI\'m a great listener, highly empathetic, and have a honed intuition through thousands of hours of experience to know how you learn best in each moment.\r\n<h5>If this sounds like something you are grooving with, let\'s chat during a <a href=\"https://katietutorsmath.acuityscheduling.com/schedule.php?appointmentType=1728850\" target=\"_blank\">New Student Consultation</a>.</h5>', 'My Philosophy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-23 00:37:27', '2016-08-23 07:37:27', '', 17, 'http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(148, 1, '2016-08-23 00:40:16', '2016-08-23 07:40:16', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\nI\'m a Minnesota-born &amp; raised girl with a Notre Dame education (math &amp; <a href=\"http://kroc.nd.edu/about-us/what-peace-studies\" target=\"_blank\">international peace studies</a>) living in Portland, Oregon.\r\n\r\nAfter two years of teaching math at a <a href=\"http://www.waldencommunityschool.com/\" target=\"_blank\">community-based secondary school</a>, I learned that although I loved teaching, it exhausted my introverted self (whatwith being on stage in front of teenagers all day).\r\n\r\nSoon after I moved to Portland. I tutored math at an alcohol &amp; drug treatment center, a homeless center, and for newly arrived immigrant and refugee students.\r\n\r\nI loved these jobs. But due to a concussion and post-concussive syndrome, I quit in spring 2016.\r\n\r\nA blessing in disguise, my <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Refuse-Choose-Interests-Passions-Hobbies/dp/1594866260\" target=\"_blank\">scanner</a> nature began to flourish and I took the opportunity to focus on entrepreneurship.\r\n\r\n(My current passion project is a platform that uses research-backed strategies to help people learn math -- specifically those preparing for the GED.)\r\n\r\nBut back to math tutoring... I tutor math because it\'s fun, I\'m very good at it, and it funds my passion project. (And I get to help people like you, and I think that\'s pretty great.)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5>And here are some details, in bullet points, so you know I\'m legit:</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>B.S. in Mathematics &amp; International Peace Studies, University of Notre Dame</li>\r\n 	<li>10 years of experience tutoring over 200 students</li>\r\n 	<li>ACT: 35 (Math: 36, Science: 36, English: 35, Reading: 33) 99th percentile</li>\r\n 	<li>GRE Quantitative: 170 (GRE Verbal: 164) 99th percentile</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5></h5>\r\n<h5>And just for fun:</h5>\r\n- I love local food. I spent a year in Spokane through <a href=\"https://jvcnorthwest.org/\" target=\"_blank\">JVC Northwest</a> working on <a href=\"http://www.catholiccharitiesfoodforall.org/\" target=\"_blank\">food access</a>. I now work at my <a href=\"http://www.montavillamarket.org/\" target=\"_blank\">neighborhood farmers market</a> in Portland crunching numbers and supporting our awesome community of volunteers.\r\n\r\n- I love nature and plan on hiking 460 miles of the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pacific_Crest_Trail\" target=\"_blank\">PCT</a> in 2018.\r\n\r\n- I\'ve had four concussions, three in 2016, and am passionate about education around care of concussions and <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Post-concussion_syndrome\" target=\"_blank\">post-concussion syndrome</a>.', 'About Me', 'Welcome to Katie Tutors Math', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-23 00:40:16', '2016-08-23 07:40:16', '', 20, 'http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/20-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(149, 1, '2016-08-23 00:41:58', '2016-08-23 07:41:58', '<strong>Are you or your child struggling with math? I am an experienced, professional, and compassionate math tutor.</strong>\r\n\r\nLet’s work together to help you achieve your goals, whether that be preparing for your next math test, completing homework, raising your grade, or a better and more thorough understanding of the material.\r\n\r\nI have a warm personality, and I foster an environment where students feel safe to try, make mistakes, and truly learn. Learning and helping others to learn is my passion.\r\n\r\nYou don’t have to struggle anymore! I tutor:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Middle School Math</li>\r\n 	<li>Algebra 1</li>\r\n 	<li>Algebra 2</li>\r\n 	<li>Geometry</li>\r\n 	<li>PreCalculus</li>\r\n 	<li>Calculus 1</li>\r\n 	<li>AP Calculus AB</li>\r\n 	<li>College Algebra</li>\r\n 	<li>Test Prep (ACT, SAT, GED, and GRE)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote>“Simply the best! Katie is a very knowledgeable and extremely patient tutor. <strong>She is a huge part of me understanding and getting through Calc 1.</strong> HIGHLY RECOMMENDED!!!”\r\n\r\n– Russell</blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAre you ready to get started?  <strong><a href=\"https://katietutorsmath.acuityscheduling.com/schedule.php?appointmentType=1728850\" target=\"_blank\">Schedule a phone consultation today</a>. </strong>I look forward to working with you soon!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>In-Person Math Tutor in Portland</h2>\r\nI offer in-person tutoring at my own location in the Montavilla neighborhood of Portland. Schedule a <a href=\"https://katietutorsmath.acuityscheduling.com/schedule.php?appointmentType=1728850\" target=\"_blank\">New Student Consultation</a> to learn more.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Online Math Tutor</h2>\r\nOnline tutoring is efficient, convenient, and effective. Learn math online! Schedule a <a href=\"https://katietutorsmath.acuityscheduling.com/schedule.php?appointmentType=1728850\" target=\"_blank\">New Student Consultation</a> to 