ou can also schedule sessions with tutors you have had in the past, making it the best of both worlds. You use a shared whiteboard and audio via your iPad, and they send you a free pen to use with your iPad!\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Limitations:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>It’s a small start-up, so at odd hours (say, the middle of the night for US time zones) there may not be any tutors available.</li>\r\n 	<li>You must use an iPad.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"qlink_container\"><a class=\"external_link\" href=\"https://www.yup.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"><b>Yup</b></a></span> (formerly MathCrunch) is great for students who have a quick homework problem. Using your mobile phone, you are instantly connected with a random tutor. You upload a photo of the problem and then have a chat box to share with the tutor.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Limitations:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>You have to use a mobile phone, and it can be difficult to get help with your math problem on such a small screen.</li>\r\n 	<li>Many of the tutors are from different countries where English is not the first language, which can make communication difficult.</li>\r\n 	<li>There is no audio or whiteboard available -- the only communication comes from the chat box.</li>\r\n 	<li>Quality of tutoring varies greatly amongst tutors.</li>\r\n 	<li>Students have no option to choose a tutor — it’s completely random each time.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThere are many other sites, but these are the ones that will get you up and running quickly.\r\n\r\nIf you are looking for a more personal relationship with your math tutor, I recommend finding an independent math tutor. You can use a search engine to find a tutor or use a site such as <a href=\"https://www.wyzant.com/\">WyzAnt</a>, <a href=\"http://www.universitytutor.com/\">UniversityTutor</a>, or <a href=\"http://www.nextguru.com/\">NextGuru</a> where tutors have profiles listed and, often, reviews. Find one that you are comfortable with and ask for a free trial session to begin with to make sure it will be a great fit for you.\r\n\r\n<em>Interested in hiring me as your online math tutor? I offer a free 30-minute trial session to all new students. Learn more <a href=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/tutoring/\">here</a>.</em>', 'The Best Online Math Tutoring Sites', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '182-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-17 11:59:17', '2016-09-17 18:59:17', '', 182, 'http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/182-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
