li>10 years of experience tutoring over 200 students</li>\r\n<li>ACT: 35 (Math: 36, Science: 36, English: 35, Reading: 33) 99th percentile</li>\r\n<li>GRE Quantitative: 170 (GRE Verbal: 164) 99th percentile</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5></h5>\r\n<h5>And just for fun:</h5>\r\n<p>- I love local food. I spent a year in Spokane through <a href=\"https://jvcnorthwest.org/\" target=\"_blank\">JVC Northwest</a> working on <a href=\"http://www.catholiccharitiesfoodforall.org/\" target=\"_blank\">food access</a>. I now work at my <a href=\"http://www.montavillamarket.org/\" target=\"_blank\">neighborhood farmers market</a> in Portland crunching numbers and supporting our awesome community of volunteers.</p>\r\n<p>- I love nature and plan on hiking 460 miles of the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pacific_Crest_Trail\" target=\"_blank\">PCT</a> in 2018.</p>\r\n<p>- I\'ve had four concussions, three in 2016, and am passionate about education around care of concussions and <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Post-concussion_syndrome\" target=\"_blank\">post-concussion syndrome</a>.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-200\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/IMG_2236-e1474320425233.jpg\" alt=\"Katie the Math Tutor\" width=\"2064\" height=\"536\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/IMG_2236-e1474320425233.jpg 2064w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/IMG_2236-e1474320425233-300x78.jpg 300w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/IMG_2236-e1474320425233-768x199.jpg 768w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/IMG_2236-e1474320425233-1024x266.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2064px) 100vw, 2064px\"></p>', 'About Me', 'Welcome to Katie Tutors Math', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-19 14:29:40', '2016-09-19 21:29:40', '', 20, 'http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/20-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
