(215, 1, '2016-09-19 15:00:16', '2016-09-19 22:00:16', '<p><strong>Are you or your child struggling with math? I am an experienced, professional, and compassionate math tutor.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Let’s work together to help you achieve your goals, whether that be preparing for your next math test, completing homework, raising your grade, or a better and more thorough understanding of the material.</p>\r\n<p>I have a warm personality, and I foster an environment where students feel safe to try, make mistakes, and truly learn. Learning and helping others to learn is my passion.</p>\r\n<p>You don’t have to struggle anymore! I tutor:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Middle School Math</li>\r\n<li>Algebra 1</li>\r\n<li>Algebra 2</li>\r\n<li>Geometry</li>\r\n<li>PreCalculus</li>\r\n<li>Calculus 1</li>\r\n<li>AP Calculus AB</li>\r\n<li>College Algebra</li>\r\n<li>Test Prep (ACT, SAT, GED, and GRE)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-110\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123.jpg\" alt=\"Math Tutor Calculator Studying\" width=\"1695\" height=\"2000\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123.jpg 1695w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123-254x300.jpg 254w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123-768x906.jpg 768w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123-868x1024.jpg 868w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1695px) 100vw, 1695px\"></p>\r\n<p>Rates for Math&nbsp;Tutoring:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>$50/hour (for one hour or more)</li>\r\n<li>$30/half-hour session</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Rates for Test Prep (SAT, ACT, GRE, GED) Tutoring:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>$75/hour (for one hour or more)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Ready to get started?</h3>\r\n<p>Schedule your free 15-minute consultation today</p>\r\n<a class=\"call-to-