(233, 1, '2016-09-25 20:36:17', '2016-09-26 03:36:17', '<strong>Are you or your child struggling with math? I am an experienced, professional, and compassionate math tutor.</strong>\r\n\r\nLet’s work together to help you achieve your goals, whether that be preparing for your next math test, completing homework, raising your grade, or a better and more thorough understanding of the material.\r\n\r\nI have a warm personality, and I foster an environment where students feel safe to try, make mistakes, and truly learn. Learning and helping others to learn is my passion.\r\n\r\nYou don’t have to struggle anymore! I tutor:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Prealgebra</li>\r\n 	<li>Algebra 1</li>\r\n 	<li>Algebra 2</li>\r\n 	<li>Geometry</li>\r\n 	<li>PreCalculus</li>\r\n 	<li>Calculus 1</li>\r\n 	<li>AP Calculus AB</li>\r\n 	<li>College Algebra</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-110\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1695px) 100vw, 1695px\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123.jpg 1695w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123-254x300.jpg 254w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123-768x906.jpg 768w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123-868x1024.jpg 868w\" alt=\"Math Tutor Calculator Studying\" width=\"1695\" height=\"2000\" />\r\n\r\nRates for Math Tutoring:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>$50/hour (for one hour or more)</li>\r\n 	<li>$30/half-hour session</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nRequirements for online tutoring:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Computer with a Webcam, Microphone, &amp; Skype</li>\r\n 	<li>Reliable Internet Connection</li>\r\n 	<li>Optional: <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2cYXZVq\">Wacom Tablet</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Ready to get started?</h3>\r\nSchedule your free 15-minute consultation today\r\n\r\n<a class=\"call-to-action-button\" title=\"Schedule\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/free-consultation/\">Schedule</a>\r\n\r\nI’ve been coming to Katie for tutoring for quite some time, and she’s finally seeing me out the door. I truly have her to thank for my success in my math courses. She has me walking away with confidence and understanding that just wasn’t there prior to our sessions. She’s always patient, kind and helpful. She makes learning the way it should be – FUN. Thanks again, Katie.\r\n\r\nAnna College Algebra, Online\r\n\r\nSimply the best! Katie is a very knowledgeable and extremely patient tutor. She is a huge part of me understanding and getting through Calc 1. HIGHLY RECOMMENDED!!!\r\n\r\nRussell College Calculus, Returning Adult Student', 'Tutoring', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '72-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-25 20:36:17', '2016-09-26 03:36:17', '', 72, 'http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/72-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
