(272, 1, '2016-12-02 18:38:46', '2016-12-03 02:38:46', '<strong>Are you or your child struggling with math? I am an experienced, professional, and compassionate math tutor.</strong>\r\n\r\nLet’s work together to help you achieve your goals, whether that be preparing for your next math test, completing homework, raising your grade, or a better and more thorough understanding of the material.\r\n\r\nI have a warm personality, and I foster an environment where students feel safe to try, make mistakes, and truly learn. Learning and helping others to learn is my passion.\r\n\r\nYou don’t have to struggle anymore! I tutor:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Middle School Math</li>\r\n 	<li>Prealgebra</li>\r\n 	<li>Algebra 1</li>\r\n 	<li>Algebra 2</li>\r\n 	<li>PreCalculus</li>\r\n 	<li>Calculus 1</li>\r\n 	<li>AP Calculus AB</li>\r\n 	<li>College Algebra</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-110\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1695px) 100vw, 1695px\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123.jpg 1695w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123-254x300.jpg 254w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123-768x906.jpg 768w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/calculator-scientific-e1474319560123-868x1024.jpg 868w\" alt=\"Math Tutor Calculator Studying\" width=\"1695\" height=\"2000\" />\r\n\r\nRates for Math Tutoring:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>55-minute sessions: $60</li>\r\n 	<li>27-minute sessions: $32</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nRequirements for online tutoring:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Computer with a Webcam, Microphone, &amp; Skype</li>\r\n 	<li>Reliable Internet Connection</li>\r\n 	<li>Optional: <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2cYXZVq\">Wacom Tablet</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Ready to get started?</h3>\r\nSchedule your free 30-minute consultation today\r\n\r\n<a class=\"call-to-action-button\" title=\"Schedule\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/free-consultation/\">Schedule</a>\r\n\r\nI’ve been coming to Katie for tutoring for quite some time, and she’s finally seeing me out the door. I truly have her to thank for my success in my math courses. She has me walking away with confidence and understanding that just wasn’t there prior to our sessions. She’s always patient, kind and helpful. She makes learning the way it should be – FUN. Thanks again, Katie.\r\n\r\nAnna College Algebra, Online\r\n\r\nSimply the best! Katie is a very knowledgeable and extremely patient tutor. She is a huge part of me understanding and getting through Calc 1. HIGHLY RECOMMENDED!!!\r\n\r\nRussell College Calculus, Returning Adult Student', 'Tutoring', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '72-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-12-02 18:38:46', '2016-12-03 02:38:46', '', 72, 'http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/72-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(273, 1, '2017-01-01 15:45:51', '2017-01-01 23:45:51', '<h4>News:</h4>\n<ul>\n 	<li>If you ever need an extra tutoring session one week, you are welcome to <a href=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/schedule-a-session/\">schedule a session</a> at your convenience! (Payment is due at time of scheduling, so have your card on hand.)</li>\n 	<li>You can always text or email me pictures of your assignments or anything that you\'d like to work on. No need to wait until our session time -- send them over a day or two early if you want.</li>\n 	<li>I use a <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00EVOXM3S/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B00EVOXM3S&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=katietutorsma-20&amp;linkId=dcd573e27dfe8561c669b4a6bf1d26a1\" target=\"_blank\">Wacom Bamboo Tablet</a><img style=\"border: none !important; margin: 0px !important;\" src=\"//ir-na.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=katietutorsma-20&amp;l=am2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B00EVOXM3S\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /> to write on the whiteboard during tutoring sessions. It\'s definitely not required for students to have one, but check out the link if you are interested. Instead of using your computer mouse, you use a special pen to write on the tablet.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2></h2>\n<h2>Policies:</h2>\n<h4></h4>\n<h4>Late Policy</h4>\nGiving the student the opportunity to learn in a tutoring session is very important to me. The student should be on time to each tutoring session to allow us as much time as possible for them to get the help they need. In the event that the student is running late, the lost time will not be made up.\n<h4>Cancellations</h4>\nThis business is my main source of income. That said, my cancellation policy is my very best attempt to balance fairness to the student and to myself. Additionally, tutoring is a valuable commitment, and showing up to each tutoring session will help the student create momentum in their learning.\n\n- I ask that you let me know about a cancellation as soon as possible. Cancellations may be made by phone (text, call, or voicemail at 503-563-4331) or email (katietutorsmath@gmail.com).\n\n- I require a 48 hour notice for a cancellation in order to not be charged. Sessions canceled with less than 48 hours notice must be paid in full.\n\n- Excessive cancellations may be reason for ending tutoring services.\n<h4>Payment</h4>\nAfter a trial period, payment is due by the first session of each month by card. Your invoice will be emailed to you by the 1st of the month. If payment is not made at the first session of the month, then the student will not be able to receive tutoring until the payment is made. Note that any tutoring sessions missed in accordance with the cancellation policy will be refunded by pro-rating the following month, unless you request otherwise.\n\nDuring the trial period, each session must be paid by the time of the session by card via an invoice you will receive by email. The trial period will be for the first three sessions unless we have agreed to something different.\n\nIf you decide to stop tutoring at any time, all remaining sessions (at least 48 hours in the future) for the month will be refunded to you in accordance with the cancellation policy.', 'Current Students', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '210-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-01-01 15:45:51', '2017-01-01 23:45:51', '', 210, 'http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/210-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(274, 1, '2016-12-02 18:59:37', '2016-12-03 02:59:37', '<h4>News:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>There will be no tutoring sessions the week of December 26 - 30.</li>\r\n 	<li>If you ever need an extra tutoring session one week, you are welcome to <a href=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/schedule-a-session/\">schedule a session</a> at your convenience! (Payment is due at time of scheduling, so have your card on hand.)</li>\r\n 	<li>I use a <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00EVOXM3S/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=1789&creative=9325&creativeASIN=B00EVOXM3S&linkCode=as2&tag=katietutorsma-20&linkId=dcd573e27dfe8561c669b4a6bf1d26a1\">Wacom Bamboo Tablet</a><img src=\"//ir-na.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=katietutorsma-20&l=am2&o=1&a=B00EVOXM3S\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\" /> to write on the whiteboard we use during sessions. It\'s definitely not required for students to have one, but check out the link if you are interested. It makes writing out those equations on our online whiteboard much easier.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2>Current Policies:</h2>\r\n<h4>Session Length</h4>\r\nHour tutoring sessions are actually 55-minute sessions. Half-hour sessions are actually 27-minute sessions. Having this short break allows me to serve each student best and stay on schedule.\r\n<h4>\r\nLate Policy</h4>\r\nGiving the student the opportunity to learn in a tutoring session is very important to me. The student should be on time to each tutoring session to allow us as much time as possible for them to get the help they need. In the event that the student is running late, the lost time will not be made up.\r\n<h4>\r\nCancellations</h4>\r\nThis business is my main source of income. That said, my cancellation policy is my very best attempt to balance fairness to the student and to myself. Additionally, tutoring is a valuable commitment, and showing up to each tutoring session will help the studen