(324, 1, '2017-01-10 11:52:05', '2017-01-10 19:52:05', 'In summer 2016 I founded Katie Tutors Math. It\'s only been a few months, but I have slogged through many resources and found everything from amazing to not-so-great resources for online math tutors.\r\n\r\nBecoming an online math tutor is a venture in entrepreneurship as well as the actual tutoring of math. I have rounded up the very best resources to help you all those aspiring online math tutors out there.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1>The 5 Best Tools for the Online Math Tutor:</h1>\r\n<h3>Share a Whiteboard: Scribblar</h3>\r\nScribblar is hands-down the most important tool in my business. With Scribblar I create \"rooms\" for each of my students. The \"room\" is a whiteboard with a unique link that has pen, highlighter, eraser, and text tools to name a few. The student and I can both see what the other is writing in real time. What makes Scribblar stand out?\r\n\r\n(1) An equation editor\r\n\r\n(2) Easy uploads of jpgs and pdfs. (Usually I have the student text or email me their assignment, and then I upload it into Scribblar.)\r\n\r\n(3) Multiple pages! You can have as many pages as you\'d like in each room, and since math problems can take up a lot of room, this is super helpful.\r\n\r\n(4) Unique links for each room. This makes it easy for each student as they just have to go to the link of their unique room at the time of our session.\r\n\r\n(5) A feature to export PDFs of the session notes so students can have a copy of the notes after each session.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nInterested? Scribblar offers a free 14-day trial. After that, plans start at $14/month. <a href=\"https://scribblar.com/\">Learn more and sign up!</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Write on the Screen: Wacom Tablet</h3>\r\nBefore I got a tablet, I was writing on Scribblar using my computer mouse, and well, let\'s just say that it wasn\'t always legible. The Wacom tablet allows you to write on the screen (via your tablet) just as you would write on a piece of paper. It\'s easy to set up, and your hands (and students) will thank you!\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3>Automate Scheduling: Acuity</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Get Paid: Square</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Manage Your Books: Quickbooks</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://fbuy.me/emO4Q\">Quickbooks</a> (click the link for 50% off for the first 6 months.)\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://scribblar.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Scribblar</a> Scribblar is an online whiteboard.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://amzn.to/2iybDjf\">Wacom tablet</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://squareup.com/i/8A4EC12A\">Square</a> (use this link to process up to $1,000 in credit card sales for free during your first 180 days)</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://acuityscheduling.com/?kw=YToxMTMwMjk0Nw%3D%3D\" target=\"_blank\">Acuity</a></li>\r\n 	<li></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHere\'s all the other tools I love that didn\'t make the top 5\r\n\r\nLogistics - Payment, Recordkeeping\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://ssqt.co/mzbSv7A\">Shoeboxed</a> (get 10% off)</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://db.tt/Op4rnPFu\">Dropbox</a> (Sign up with this link and we\'ll both receive 500 MB of bonus space.)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nProductivity\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Todoist</li>\r\n 	<li>Trello</li>\r\n 	<li>Evernote</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://workflowy.com/invite/3675719a.lnx\">Workflowy</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMarketing\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Wordpress.org (recommend themes)</li>\r\n 	<li>peek.usertesting</li>\r\n 	<li>Canva</li>\r\n 	<li>Pixabay (stock photos)</li>\r\n 	<li>Google Analytics</li>\r\n 	<li>Hootsuite?</li>\r\n 	<li>Mailchimp</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAudio/Video\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://amzn.to/2iUnBjm\">Yeti</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Screencastomatic</li>\r\n 	<li>(what\'s the one I use now?)</li>\r\n 	<li>Videoscribe</li>\r\n 	<li>Skype</li>\r\n 	<li>Google Hangouts</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://amzn.to/2iFeMeg\">Webcam</a> I use</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMath Resources\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.ixl.com/\" target