(376, 1, '2017-02-02 10:09:53', '2017-02-02 18:09:53', '<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-374\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Online-Math-Tutor-Katie-Tutors-Math-2.jpeg\" alt=\"Online Math Tutor Katie Tutors Math\" width=\"1400\" height=\"409\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Online-Math-Tutor-Katie-Tutors-Math-2.jpeg 1400w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Online-Math-Tutor-Katie-Tutors-Math-2-300x88.jpeg 300w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Online-Math-Tutor-Katie-Tutors-Math-2-768x224.jpeg 768w, http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Online-Math-Tutor-Katie-Tutors-Math-2-1024x299.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\"></p>\r\n<p><strong>Are you or your child struggling with math? I am an experienced, professional, and compassionate math tutor.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Let’s work together to help you achieve your goals, whether that be preparing for your next math test, completing homework, raising your grade, or a better and more thorough understanding of the material.</p>\r\n<p>I have a warm personality, and I foster an environment where students feel safe to try, make mistakes, and truly learn. Learning and helping others to learn is my passion.</p>\r\n<p>I love making math understandable for students and fostering an environment where students develop a growth mindset and gain confidence in their math skills and their ability to do hard things.</p>\r\n<p>We use Skype or Google Hangouts to see and hear each other and an online whiteboard (scribblar) to see what the other person is writing in real time.</p>\r\n<p>You don’t have to struggle anymore! I tutor:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Middle School Math</li>\r\n<li>Prealgebra</li>\r\n<li>Algebra 1</li>\r\n<li>Algebra 2</li>\r\n<li>PreCalculus</li>\r\n<li>Calculus 1</li>\r\n<li>AP Calculus AB</li>\r\n<li>College Algebra</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Requirements for online tutoring:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Computer with a Webcam, Microphone, &amp;&nbsp;Skype</li>\r\n<li>Reliable Internet Connection</li>\r\n<li>Optional: <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2cYXZVq\">Wacom Tablet</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Rates</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>60 minute session - $60</li>\r\n<li>30 minute session - $32</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- Featured Video Plus v2.3.3 -->\r\n<iframe width=\"533\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/n9ExGZkDGOA?width=642&amp;height=300&amp;autoplay&amp;origin=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%3A8888%2Fktm_wp\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n<img class=\"fvp-onload\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/wp-content/plugins/featured-video-plus/img/playicon.png\" alt=\"Featured Video Play Icon\" onload=\"(function() {(\'initFeaturedVideoPlus\' in this) &amp;&amp; (\'function\' === typeof initFeaturedVideoPlus) &amp;&amp; initFeaturedVideoPlus();})();\"><h3 class=\"widget-title\"><a href=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/welcome-to-katie-tutors-math/\" title=\"Welcome to Katie Tutors Math\">Welcome to Katie Tutors Math</a></h3><p></p>			\r\n<h3>You don\'t have to struggle with math anymore</h3>\r\n<p>Schedule your free consultation today</p>\r\n<a class=\"call-to-action-button\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/free-consultation/\" title=\"Schedule\">Schedule</a>\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">What Students Say</h3>		\r\n<p>I’ve been coming to Katie for tutoring for quite some time, and she’s finally seeing me out the door. I truly have her to thank for my success in my mathematics courses. She has me walking away with confidence and understanding that just wasn’t there prior to our sessions. She’s always patient, kind and helpful. She makes learning the way it should be – FUN. Thanks again, Katie.</p>\r\n<span>Anna</span>\r\nCollege Algebra Student		\r\n<p>My son\'s Geometry grade turned from a ‘D’ to an ‘A’! Katie was a very professional tutor for my son in his first year of high school. He was struggling with Geometry and Spanish as a freshman. Due to Katie’s great tutoring skills, my son is an honor roll student. I was very pleased with Katie targeting his weak areas and turning his grades around!!! Job well done!\r\n</p>\r\n<span>Jimita</span>\r\nParent', 'Katie Tutors Math', 'Online Math Tutoring by a Notre Dame Grad. Free 30 minute consultation!\r\nPrealgebra, Algebra, Geometry, Trigonometry, Precalculus, Calculus. ', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-02-02 10:09:53', '2017-02-02 18:09:53', '', 10, 'http://localhost:8888/ktm_wp/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
